OL,4,C'abhorrent' post about supporter's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA Sheffield Wednesday fan has been
OL,8,Fbanned for life, sacked from his job
OL,9,Fand charged by police over an
OL,10,F"abhorrent" social media post about
OL,11,Fthe death of a rival supporter.
OL,13,FThe club took action after a post on X
OL,14,Fappearing to mock the death of West
OL,15,FBrom fan Mark Townsend.
OL,17,FMr Townsend, 57, suffered a medical
OL,18,Femergency in the Leppings Lane end and
OL,19,Flater died when the two sides met at
OL,20,FHillsborough on Saturday.
