OL,7,FThe social media post appeared to make
OL,8,Freference to the deaths of 97
OL,9,FLiverpool fans during the 1989
OL,10,FHillsborough tragedy. The account has
OL,11,Fsince been suspended.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Wednesday confirmed a
OL,14,F"lifetime ban from all club activities
OL,15,Fand premises for the individual
OL,16,Fresponsible for an abhorrent social
OL,17,Fmedia post".
