OL,7,FIt added: "We condemn absolutely this
OL,8,Foutrageous behaviour and underline our
OL,9,Fzero tolerance policy towards unlawful
OL,10,Factivity on all social media platforms.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with the loved
OL,13,Fones of Mr Townsend and the wider West
OL,14,FBromwich Albion community at this
OL,15,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police said a 55-year-
OL,18,Fold man has been charged with
OL,19,Fmalicious communications and is due to
OL,20,Fappear at Sheffield Magistrates' Court
OL,21,Fon 14 October.
