OL,7,FMeanwhile, construction firm Wates
OL,8,FGroup confirmed that it had sacked an
OL,9,Femployee over the incident.
OL,11,FIn a statement the company said: "The
OL,12,Fcomments made over the weekend are
OL,13,Funacceptable and completely at odds
OL,14,Fwith our values as a company."
OL,16,FWest Brom said their players would
OL,17,Fwear black armbands and hold an
OL,18,Fapplause in Mr Townsend's memory
OL,19,Fduring their game against
OL,20,FMiddlesbrough on Tuesday.
